    "quote": "Stop talking to yourself, Wade. They'll think you're crazy. Well, crazier… heh… and, y'know, you're not crazy. That would just be.. ridiculous! You know who's crazy? You! Yeah, I'm talkin' to you, kid. I know you're playing and you're crazy because you're playing as me! As Deadpool! Haha, hey, fine, take a… take a deep breath.",
